        "sendTo": "={{$json.managerEmail}}",
        "subject": "=Training Escalation: {{ $json.partnerName }} has an overdue training",
        "message": "=<p>Hello,</p>\n\n<p>This is an automated escalation from the Partner Training Operations System.</p>\n\n<p>The following learner has exceeded the training deadline and requires follow-up.</p>\n\n<table border=\"1\" cellpadding=\"6\" cellspacing=\"0\">\n<tr>\n<td><b>Partner</b></td>\n<td>{{ $json.partnerName }}</td>\n</tr>\n\n<tr>\n<td><b>Company</b></td>\n<td>{{ $json.company }}</td>\n</tr>\n\n<tr>\n<td><b>Training Program</b></td>\n<td>{{ $json.trainingProgram }}</td>\n</tr>\n\n<tr>\n<td><b>Status</b></td>\n<td>{{ $json.trainingStatus }}</td>\n</tr>\n\n<tr>\n<td><b>Reminder Count</b></td>\n<td>{{ $json.reminderCount }}</td>\n</tr>\n\n</table>\n\n<br>\n\n<p>Please contact the learner and assist them in completing the required training.</p>\n\n<p>Thank you.</p>\n\n<hr>\n\n<p><i>This email was automatically generated by the Partner Training Operations Platform.</i></p>",
        "options": {}
      },
